text: Zymic Jaranilla (born 20 May 2004) is a Filipino child actor. Zymic was mostly seen in GMA Network and appeared once in TV5. His first appearance in TV was Felina: Prinsesa ng mga Pusa, which it broadcast in TV5. == Personal life == Zymic is the youngest and the 3rd sibling within the Jaranilla family. He lives with his father, his grandmother, and his two older brothers.
